    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine starts reliably and runs smoothly, while the transmission provides steady, predictable shifts. Both the exterior and interior have been kept clean, showing only the minor signs of regular use you would expect from a car of this age. It's a solid, dependable choice for anyone looking for a vehicle that is ready for the road without any immediate mechanical concerns.",
