    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior still carries a great shine, although you will find some minor surface scratches and a few small door dings expected with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only light wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, it performs very well, offering a smooth ride and dependable performance for its next owner.",
